I have ordained a lantern for míne anoínted. 19 As for his enemies, I shall clóthe them with sháme;
but upon himself sháll his crown floúrish. 20 Glory be to the Father, and tó the Són,
and to the Hóly Ghóst; 21 As it was in the beginning, † is now, and éver sháll be,
world wíthout énd. Amen.

